<para>Livre sterling anglais : &#163;.
</para>
</listitem></varlistentry><varlistentry><term><indexterm role="fn"><primary>\quotedblbase (&#8222;)</primary></indexterm><literal>\quotedblbase (&#8222;)</literal>
